### Geofence Test API Requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/geofences/health

### Create Circular Geofence - Downtown Office
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/geofences
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "partnerCompanyId": 1,
  "name": "Downtown Office",
  "description": "Main office zone - alerts on entry and exit",
  "type": "CIRCLE",
  "centerLatitude": 11.556374,
  "centerLongitude": 104.928206,
  "radiusMeters": 500,
  "alertType": "BOTH",
  "active": true
}

### Create Polygon Geofence - Warehouse District
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/geofences
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "partnerCompanyId": 1,
  "name": "Warehouse District",
  "description": "Industrial zone - entry alerts only",
  "type": "POLYGON",
  "geoJsonCoordinates": "[[11.550, 104.920], [11.550, 104.930], [11.560, 104.930], [11.560, 104.920], [11.550, 104.920]]",
  "alertType": "ENTER",
  "active": true
}

### Create Speed-Limited Zone
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/geofences
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "partnerCompanyId": 1,
  "name": "School Zone",
  "description": "Reduced speed area - 30 km/h limit",
  "type": "CIRCLE",
  "centerLatitude": 11.562000,
  "centerLongitude": 104.935000,
  "radiusMeters": 300,
  "alertType": "BOTH",
  "speedLimitKmh": 30,
  "active": true
}

### Create Restricted Area (Exit Alerts Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/geofences
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "partnerCompanyId": 1,
  "name": "Restricted Area",
  "description": "High security zone - exit monitoring",
  "type": "CIRCLE",
  "centerLatitude": 11.548000,
  "centerLongitude": 104.925000,
  "radiusMeters": 400,
  "alertType": "EXIT",
  "active": true
}

### Get All Active Geofences
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/geofences?companyId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Geofences Paginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/geofences/paginated?companyId=1&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Specific Geofence
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/geofences/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update Geofence
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/geofences/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "partnerCompanyId": 1,
  "name": "Downtown Office (Updated)",
  "description": "Main office zone - updated description",
  "type": "CIRCLE",
  "centerLatitude": 11.556374,
  "centerLongitude": 104.928206,
  "radiusMeters": 600,
  "alertType": "BOTH",
  "active": true
}

### Delete Geofence (Soft Delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/geofences/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Test Coordinates for Crossing Detection
# These coordinates can be used to simulate driver movement
# Downtown Office Center: 11.556374, 104.928206 (radius 500m)
# Point Inside: 11.556500, 104.928300
# Point Outside: 11.560000, 104.935000
# Point on Boundary: 11.560874, 104.928206

